# Wanderlust
An API that maps smart phones to country based mobile phone providers

# Group Countries
The list of countries that have mobile phone carriers

## Countries Collection [/countries]
### List all Countries[GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {"data":[
            {
                "id": 1,
                "name": "United States",
                "abbr": "USA"
            },
            {
                "id": 2,
                "name": "China",
                "abbr": "CN"
            }
        ]}


### Create a Country [POST]
+ Request (application/json)

        { "name": "Japan", "abbr": "JPN" }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

        {"data":{ "id": 3, "name": "Japan", "abbr": "JPN"}}

## Country [/countries/{id}]
A single Country object with all its details

+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `2`) ... Numeric `id` of the Country to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a Country [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            { "id": 2, "name": "China", "abbr": "CN" }
            
### Remove a Country [DELETE]
+ Response 204


