# Group Reports  
Return the reports on phones and networks

## Reports [/reports?phone={phone_id}&country={country_id}]

+ Parameters
    + phone_id (number, `123`, required) - ID of the phone.
    + country_id (number, `321`, required) - ID of the country.
    
